        Parameters:
        params - the parameter object for the MapDigesterLocator
        longitudeStart - the start longitude
        latitudeStart - the start latitude
        longitudeStop - the stop longitude
        latitudeStop - the stop latitude
        stepSize - the step size in which between the start and stop of the longitude and latitude should be iterated
        mapsImageUrlPattern - the url pattern which is used with the String.format-method to generate a request-url for Google Maps with the specified longitude and latitude.
